{"type":"text","timestamp":1778607650391,"sessionID":"ses_1e2f7031dffeWZz71U9TRA4SPo","part":{"id":"prt_e1d46a2b5001SXM7hWnJ0oF201","messageID":"msg_e1d3f27b9001KGNMDx0f6ltCvH","sessionID":"ses_1e2f7031dffeWZz71U9TRA4SPo","type":"text","text":"I will address issue #3457 by adding the VCCF vasculature terms to the UBERON ontology. I'll process them in batches grouped by organ.\n\nFirst, I'll start with the terms related to the **eye**:\n- anterior ciliary artery\n- short posterior ciliary artery\n- long posterior ciliary artery\n- anterior ciliary vein\n\nI will research their definitions, parents, and appropriate relationships.","time":{"start":1778607628981,"end":1778607650390}}}
